DROP EXTERNAL TABLE F_MFRHistory;

CREATE EXTERNAL TABLE F_MFRHistory (
	[H_MFRLocationKey] nvarchar(4000),
	[H_MFRCurrentDepotCode] nvarchar(4000),
	[H_MFRLocationDate] datetime2(7),
	[H_MFRBelongsDateFrom] datetime2(7),
	[H_MFRBelongsDateTo] datetime2(7),
	[H_MFRHorse] nvarchar(4000),
	[H_MFRVehicleStatus] nvarchar(4000),
	[H_MFRBranch] nvarchar(4000),
	[H_MFRModel] nvarchar(4000),
	[H_MFREquipment] nvarchar(4000),
	[H_MFRChassisNumber] nvarchar(4000),
	[H_MFRVehicleColour] nvarchar(4000),
	[H_MFREngineNumber] nvarchar(4000),
	[H_MFRApplication] nvarchar(4000),
	[H_MFRDivision] nvarchar(4000),
	[H_MFRRecommendedTyreSize] nvarchar(4000),
	[H_MFRAlternativeTyreSize] nvarchar(4000),
	[H_MFRDepotCode] nvarchar(4000),
	[H_MFRExpiryDateOnLicence] datetime2(7),
	[H_MFRLicenceFee] numeric(19,6),
	[H_MFRGrossVehicleMass] numeric(19,6),
	[H_MFRTareWeight] numeric(19,6),
	[H_MFRPayload] numeric(19,6),
	[H_MFRPeopleCarrier] nvarchar(4000),
	[H_MFRTotalNoOfTyres] int,
	[H_MFRNoOfSteeringAxleTyres] int,
	[H_MFRNoOfRearAxleTyres] int,
	[H_MFRExternalBodyLength_M] numeric(19,6),
	[H_MFRFleetNo] nvarchar(4000),
	[H_MFRExternalBodyWidth_M] numeric(19,6),
	[H_MFRExternalBodyHeight_M] numeric(19,6),
	[H_MFRInternalBodyLength_M] numeric(19,6),
	[H_MFRInternalBodyWidth_M] numeric(19,6),
	[H_MFRInternalBodyHeight_M] numeric(19,6),
	[H_MFRInternalVolumetricCapacity] numeric(19,6),
	[H_MFRMakeOfBody] nvarchar(4000),
	[H_MFRAvailbilityForAdvertising] nvarchar(4000),
	[H_MFRAdvertisingOrSignwritingOn] nvarchar(4000),
	[H_MFRFrameworkInstalledForFlexiMount] nvarchar(4000),
	[H_MFRCcClass/TypeOfVehicle] nvarchar(4000),
	[H_MFRDiesel/Petrol] nvarchar(4000),
	[H_MFRTankCapacity] int,
	[H_MFRKMRangeOnFullTankFuel] numeric(19,6),
	[H_MFRTargetConsumption] numeric(19,6),
	[H_MFRKMs/Litre] numeric(19,6),
	[H_MFREngineProtection/IdleRevs] nvarchar(4000),
	[H_MFROriginalFinanceCompany] nvarchar(4000),
	[H_MFRContractNumber] nvarchar(4000),
	[H_MFRRegNo] nvarchar(4000),
	[H_MFRContractStartDate] datetime2(7),
	[H_MFRContractEndDate] datetime2(7),
	[H_MFRFirstInstalmentDate] datetime2(7),
	[H_MFRPreviousOwnershipOfVehicle] nvarchar(4000),
	[H_MFRFleetHaulNumber] nvarchar(4000),
	[H_MFROldRegNo] nvarchar(4000),
	[H_MFRETollClass] nvarchar(4000),
	[H_MFRAssetStatus] nvarchar(4000),
	[H_MFRYearModel] int,
	[H_MFRMake] nvarchar(4000),
	[H_MFRSeries] nvarchar(4000),
	[H_MFRPTName] nvarchar(4000),
	[H_MFRAssetCode] nvarchar(4000),
	[H_MFRVehicleFinanced] nvarchar(4000),
	[H_MFRHasRegChanged] nvarchar(4000),
	[H_MFRBackDoorWidth] numeric(19,6),
	[H_MFRBackDoorHeight] numeric(19,6)
	)
	WITH (
	LOCATION = 'DataLake/Structured/Facts/F_MFRHISTORY.parquet',
	DATA_SOURCE = [synapse_citylogisticsstorage_dfs_core_windows_net],
	FILE_FORMAT = [SynapseParquetFormat]
	)
GO



SELECT TOP 100 * FROM dbo.F_MFRHistory
GO
